name: Catfish Keith Tickets - 9th November - Birmingham UK
description:
The incomparable string-twanging master of country blues and slide guitar is back, direct from the US of A. We guarantee you WILL be amazed!!

Playing at The Tower of Song, Cotteridge, Birmingham, this is a unique opportunity to see a modern legend in an intimate and atmospheric setting.

Please be aware that we are a small venue, so numbers are strictly limited - we strongly recommend buying your ticket in well advance to ensure admission - when the "House Full" signs go up on the night, don't say you weren't told already!!

Venue - Tower of Song Cafe Bar, Pershore Road South, Cotteridge Birmingham

www.towerofsong.co.uk
